Network packet sniffer via libpcap. 

1. Avaliable keys:
  -h or --help: Print help information;
  -d or --device: Specify device to sniff;
  -f or --filter: Specify filter string;
  -l or --list: Print list of the devices.

2. Usage:
  There is two main use-cases:
    a) snif -l : Get list of the device;
    b) snif -d <device> -f <filter> : Sniff the <device> with the <filter> string.
